        <item>
            <title>騰訊新遊戲《Light of Motiram》，被指抄襲《地平線》+《芒亨》+《幻獸帕魯》</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:00:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokemon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[騰訊]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277858</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>中國騰訊旗下子公司 Polaris Quest 所開發的新遊戲《Light of Motiram》最近引起爭議，有輿論指遊戲抄襲 Sony 的經典作品《Horizon Zero Dawn》（地平線，期待黎明）與《Horizon Forbidden West》（地平線，西域禁地）。有玩家指遊戲畫面、玩法設計、故事背景及角色設置，也與 Sony 的《Horizon》系列有著諸多雷同之處。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/l11732793630767.jpg 888w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p>《Light of Motiram》是一款多人在線開放世界生存遊戲，背景設定在自然與機械交織的末日世界，玩家在充斥著機械生物的荒野中重建人類文明，並與「機械獸」對抗求生。從預告片及遊戲畫面來看，遊戲中的女主角形象及其動作設計，幾乎與《Horizon》中的艾洛伊如出一轍。而遊戲中的機械生物，無論是其造型、特徵，還是戰鬥方式，均與《Horizon》中的機械獸極為相似，甚至整體後末日的風格也有著驚人的相近之處。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278095" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125637.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p>眾多玩家指出，《Light of Motiram》在遊戲機制、基建建設資源收集等方面，與《Monster Hunter》及《Palworld》也有顯著的相似性。尤其是《Palworld》涉嫌「抄襲」《Pokemon》元素而一度引發爭議後，類似情況無疑再度成為焦點。更有玩家在 Steam 平台上直言不諱指這款遊戲幾乎可以視作《Horizon 3》，並用「令人作嘔的抄襲」來形容其設計。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Disgusting Rip-Off</p><p>— Pirate King (@Maanlosi) <a href="https://twitter.com/Maanlosi/status/1862086620561789224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">November 28, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125642.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125648.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p>目前遊戲開發方尚未對這些指控給予正式回應，但隨著爭議的不斷升溫，無疑再度點燃遊戲業界對創意原創性與版權保護的討論。作為《Horizon》系列的發行商，Sony 會否對此事採取法律行動亦成為了業界與玩家熱議的焦點。值得一提的是，Sony 目前正開發一款基於《Horizon》世界觀的多人在線服務遊戲。儘管爭議未息，《Light of Motiram》仍會於 2025 年在 PC 與手機平台推出，支援跨平台遊玩。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125653.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129125700.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：IGN</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="h-lol-1732793707107-ezgif.com-gif-to-mp4-converter (1)" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1034405724?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲影片來源：IGN</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.ign.com/articles/new-tencent-game-accused-of-ripping-off-sonys-horizon-series?">IGN</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
