        <item>
            <title>【報價】vivo X200 系列香港正式發佈，港行靚鏡手機 + 眩光問題有解決？+ 開售詳情公佈</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/vivo-x200series-hk-launch/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=vivo-x200series-hk-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/29/vivo-x200series-hk-launch/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:59:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[vivo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[X200 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1277998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>vivo 在一個月前，就在中國發佈了新一代的旗艦手機 X200 系列，而當中的 X200 及 X200 Pro 之後亦宣佈會推出國際版，而這兩部 vivo 新機今日就正式在香港發佈。究竟這部配備超靚「蔡司」鏡的手機表現如何？之前的眩光問題有沒有解決？開售詳情如何？就讓 Edward 帶大家到現場看看吧。</p><h2>新一代旗艦靚鏡依然</h2><p>今次 vivo 推出的 X200 及 X200 Pro，基本上與國行的 X200 及 X200 Pro 一樣，同樣配備了超靚的「蔡司」鏡頭，分別是前者配備了均為 5,000 萬像素的主攝鏡、超廣角鏡及超級長焦鏡，而後者就除了配備相同的超廣角鏡外，亦內建了擁有大感光元件的 5,000 萬像素主攝鏡及高達 2 億像素的 APO 超級長焦鏡。另外，兩機均內建了 MTK 天璣 9400 處理器，亦均支援 IP68 及 IP69 防水防塵級數。電量方面，X200 內建了 5,800mAh 容量電池並支援 90W 有線快充，而 X200 Pro 除了內建更大容量的 6,000mAh 電池外，亦支援 90W 有線及 30W 無線快充。至於較高階的 X200 Pro 的完整使用體驗，大家可以 <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/vivo-x200pro-chinaversion-review/review-2/">&lt;點按此&gt;</a> 瀏覽筆者早前測試的國行版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_123923-1.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲vivo 今日在香港正式推出 X200（左）及 X200 Pro（右）兩部旗艦靚鏡手機。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135822.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲兩部 X200 系列同樣依然配備了「蔡司」靚鏡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130439.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130510.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過相機規格上自然是較貴較高階的 X200 Pro 更加吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125613.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 系列亦是現時市場少有仍會內建自家定製影像晶片的手機機款。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125445.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲X200 及 X200 Pro 均內建了 MTK 最新推出的天璣 9400 處理器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125755.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲兩機亦同樣支援 IP68 及 IP69 防水防塵級數。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125749.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，兩部 X 系新機均內建了大容量電池，尤其是較高階的 X200 Pro，不但容量較高，亦同時支援有線及無線快充。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_125826_.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲亦與其他旗艦手機一樣，支援不同的 AI 功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130523.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130555.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於 X200 及 X200 Pro 的其他特點及功能，大家可參晚上面兩張相片。</p><h2>眩光問題有否解決？似乎有改善</h2><p>另外，早前國行版本 vivo X200 Pro 推出時，有些用家就反映手機雖然鏡頭質素出色，但就似乎出現官方稱為「畫外眩光」的問題。官方亦承認因為今代鏡頭模組比上代薄，但就塞入超大感光元件及超大光圈（f/1.57）的主攝鏡，導致更大光圈及進光量亦帶來更易觸發畫外眩光，確實屬於硬件上設計的問題。今日香港記招筆者亦向 vivo 查詢港行推出時此問題有否解決？而香港 vivo 亦承認確實有此問題，但其實官方會在今年內向用家以 OTA 形式發送可以減輕或消除眩光的軟件，屆時用家安裝後眩光問題就有望可改善。不過官方表示如果用上此補丁，就可能會犧牲一定像素，所以如何選擇就視乎用家的個人喜好了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132734.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_132837.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲vivo 已為 X200 系列推出了改善畫外眩光問題的修改檔，香港 vivo 表示在今年內會以 OTA 形式推送給用家安裝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_133040.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安裝後，在相機設定中會見到「拍照眩光減弱」功能，開啟後官方表示可以有效減弱之前的眩光問題，不過是否屬實就有待日後借得真機後再為大家實試了。</p><h2>開售詳情公佈香港「獨家」有藍色</h2><p>至於開售詳情方面，vivo X200 及 X200 Pro 均已開始接受預訂，並會在 12 月 1 日，即係本週日正式開賣。定價方面，X200 為 $6,998，而 X200 Pro 則為 $8,998。值得留意的是，港行 X200 設有星雲黑及森林綠兩隻顏色，而 X200 Pro 方面除了設有所有有開售國際版均有售的星雲黑及地玄鈦色外，更暫時是中國市場以外「獨家」有賣海洋藍版本，而筆者現場望過，這個海洋藍色確實有點特別，不過如果真要説，筆者覺得地玄鈦色似乎更加低調漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_130714.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲推出詳情方面，vivo X200 定價為 $6,998，而 X200 Pro 定價則為 $8,998。前者設有星雲黑及森林綠兩隻顏色，而後者就設有星雲黑、地玄鈦及海洋藍 3 款顏色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_131822.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當中尤以海洋藍這款機身顏色，香港是中國地區以外唯一有推出此顏色的地方，不過筆者現場望過實機，確實特別但不算太吸睛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241128_135802.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲相對地筆者覺得地玄鈦色似乎更加漂亮，不過設計就相對較低調。</p><br /><b>
]]>
